    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Certainly, because even if these islands were wiped out, we of the free world would continue the fight from Canada or America, and we should win it in the end.<p></p> After all, it is not just the safety of these islands with which we are concerned; we are concerned with the whole idea of the free way of life, that <em>versus</em> Communism, and in that we are at one.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
