                Mr. Nutting
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f04a5d24-e262-4aaa-b6ce-cf9723651297" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
