ams, W. T. (Hammersmith, S.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Oliver, G. H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Snow, J. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Willis, E. G.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Orbach, M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Sorensen, R. W,</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wilson, Rt. Hon. Harold (Huyton)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Oswald, T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Soskice, Rt. Hon, Sir Frank</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Winterbottom, Ian (Nottingham, C.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Owen, W. J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Sparks, J. A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Winterbottom, Richard (Brightside)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Padley, W. E.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Steele, T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Woodburn, Rt. Hon. A.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Paget, R. T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stewart, Michael (Fulham, E.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wyatt, W. L.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Paling, Rt. Hon. W. (Dearne Valley)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stokes, Rt. Hon. R. R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Yates, V. F.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Paling, Will T. (Dewsbury)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Strachey, Rt. Hon. J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Younger, Rt. Hon. K.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Palmer, A. M. F.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Strauss, Rt. Hon. George (Vauxhall)</td></p><p class="Division"> <t